T|TIER|1|Decision Queue 2.0 detail:
T|TIER|2|mc becomes the hy filter: reads all ag output, decides what reaches ce
T|TIER|3|Defer/snooze w/ Telegram nudges via existing cron → send_message plumbing
T|TIER|4|"Clear my queue" one-by-one mode
T|TIER|5|Reduction stat: "mc filtered X% — 7 items need you"
T|TIER|6|Sources: Task Board, sl Approvals, Software Pipeline, (future) em
T|TIER|7|
T|TIER|8|Software Pipeline detail:
T|TIER|9|dv ag: cr PR only, never push to master
T|TIER|10|qn: automated QA gate (rc-doctor + lint + typecheck)
T|TIER|11|ce reviews after QA passes → merge
T|TIER|12|Failed QA → back to Planning (not In Progress)
T|TIER|13|Portfolio view: one card per project/repo w/ progress %
T|TIER|14|
T|TIER|0|[TABLE:4×4]
T|TIER|1|Task Board detail:
T|TIER|2|Proposed → Backlog → This Week → rv → Done
T|TIER|3|No "In Progress" column (Live Activity tracker replaces it)
T|TIER|4|Two yellow gates escalate to Decision Queue
T|TIER|5|Learning: auto-ap safe task tp after 3 successes
T|TIER|6|
