T|TIER|8|3D force-directed graph (replace current 2D graph)
T|TIER|9|Library tab: browse/search all MD files by category
T|TIER|10|Visibility scoping: Private / Team / vt / Cross-vt
T|TIER|11|"What the ag don't know" gaps panel → actionable tasks
