T|NOT |0|YouTube Studio / cn Pipeline / Shorts → yv is e-commerce, not a cn creator
T|NOT |1|Consulting CRM / Cinematic Sites → rv md differenct
T|NOT |2|3D Office → Fun gimmick, zero business value for yv
